commit.message:
linux.h (CPP_PREDEFINES): Add -D__i386__.

        * From Christian Gafton:
        * i386/linux.h (CPP_PREDEFINES): Add -D__i386__.
        * sparc/linux.h (CPP_PREDEFINES): Add -D__sparc__.
        * sparc/linux64.h (CPP_PREDEFINES): Add -D__sparc__.

From-SVN: r23485
